caption:
🔬 Did you know that hydrogen sulfide producers use hydrogen to create hydrogen sulfide? This could make hydrogen levels appear lower, leading to a false negative if you test with an outdated 2-gas breath test. Trio-Smart measures hydrogen sulfide, hydrogen, and methane, ensuring you get the complete picture of your gut health.
